  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for ffmpeg-7",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for ffmpeg-7 fixes the following issues:\n\n- Updated to version 7.1.2:\n  * avcodec/librsvgdec: fix compilation with librsvg 2.50.3\n  * libavfilter/af_firequalizer: Add check for av_malloc_array()\n  * avcodec/libsvtav1: unbreak build with latest svtav1\n  * avformat/hls: Fix Youtube AAC\n  * Various bugfixes.\n  * CVE-2025-7700: Fixed NULL Pointer Dereference in ALS Decoder (bsc#1246790)\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
